8struct nv50_disp_chan {
9 const struct nv50_disp_chan_func *func;
10 const struct nv50_disp_chan_mthd *mthd;
11 struct nv50_disp_root *root;
12 int chid;
13 int head;
14
15 struct nvkm_object object;
16};
17
18struct nv50_disp_chan_func {
19 void *(*dtor)(struct nv50_disp_chan *);
20 int (*init)(struct nv50_disp_chan *);
21 void (*fini)(struct nv50_disp_chan *);
22 int (*child_get)(struct nv50_disp_chan *, int index,
23 struct nvkm_oclass *);
24 int (*child_new)(struct nv50_disp_chan *, const struct nvkm_oclass *,
25 void *data, u32 size, struct nvkm_object **);
26};

59 u32 addr;

65 } data[];
66};
